Vendored third-party code
-------------------------

This package includes a vendored copy of Ultralytics 8.3.2 in
`napari_microplate/_vendor/ultralytics/`, modified to support single-channel
grayscale input (`ch=1`) at inference time for well detection.

  Original project:  https://github.com/ultralytics/ultralytics
